<section class="link-techs-section text-center position-relative">
  <div class="container d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center gap-3">
    <header class="link-features-title tech-title d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-end">
      <h2 class="linear-text-gradient">Les technologies derrière L'INK</h2>
      <p class="text-white mb-2">Une stack moderne pour des performances optimales</p>
      <p class="techs-description text-white-50 mb-0">
        L’INK s’appuie sur des outils robustes et reconnus pour garantir fiabilité, rapidité et évolutivité.<br>
        Chaque technologie a été choisie pour répondre aux besoins des tatoueurs et de leurs clients.
      </p>
    </header>
    <div class="skills-container w-100 d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
      <div class="skill-container-line d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center gap-3">
        <div class="tech-glass-container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
          <div class="skill-glass-container glass-effect d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <%= image_tag "ruby-logo.webp", class: "w-100 object-fit-contain", alt: "Logo Ruby", loading: "lazy" %>
          </div>
          <span class="tech-badge">Ruby</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-glass-container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
          <div class="skill-glass-container glass-effect d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <%= image_tag "rails-logo.webp", alt: "Logo Ruby on Rails", loading: "lazy" %>
          </div>
          <span class="tech-badge">Rails</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-glass-container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
          <div class="skill-glass-container glass-effect d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <%= image_tag "postgresql-logo.webp", alt: "Logo PostgreSQL", loading: "lazy" %>
          </div>
          <span class="tech-badge">PostgreSQL</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-glass-container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
          <div class="skill-glass-container glass-effect d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <%= image_tag "git-logo.webp", alt: "Logo Git", loading: "lazy" %>
          </div>
          <span class="tech-badge">Git</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mockup-teck-container position-relative d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center">
        <div class="glow-circle-pink" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="glow-circle-orange" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <%= image_tag 'mokup-iphone-link.webp', loading: "lazy", alt: "Mockup L'INK sur iPhone" %>
        <p class="mockup-caption text-white-50 mt-1 mb-0">
          Interface mobile intuitive et design épuré pour une expérience utilisateur optimale.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-container-line d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center gap-3">
        <div class="tech-glass-container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
          <div class="skill-glass-container glass-effect d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center p-2">
            <%= image_tag "html-logo.webp", alt: "Logo HTML5", loading: "lazy" %>
          </div>
          <span class="tech-badge">HTML5</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-glass-container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
          <div class="skill-glass-container glass-effect d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <%= image_tag "css-logo.webp", alt: "Logo CSS3", loading: "lazy" %>
          </div>
          <span class="tech-badge">CSS3</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-glass-container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
          <div class="skill-glass-container glass-effect d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <%= image_tag "java-script-logo.webp", alt: "Logo JavaScript", loading: "lazy" %>
          </div>
          <span class="tech-badge">JavaScript</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tech-glass-container d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
          <div class="skill-glass-container glass-effect d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
            <%= image_tag "bootstrap-logo.webp", alt: "Logo Bootstrap", loading: "lazy" %>
          </div>
          <span class="tech-badge">Bootstrap</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="techs-footer text-white-50">
      <span>
        Toutes ces technologies sont combinées pour offrir une application rapide, sécurisée et agréable à utiliser.<br>
        <strong>L’INK</strong> évolue constamment pour intégrer les meilleures innovations du web.
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
